Name: Call and meeting type
Description: The activity type of the engagement
Options: Sales - Cold Call; Sales - Discovery; Sales - Demo; Sales - Follow Up; Sales - Negotiation; Sales - Other; LS - Executive Onboarding; LS - Technical Onboarding 1; LS - Studio Tour; LS - Goal Setting; LS - Performance Reviews; LS - Check-in; LS - Support; LS - F2F; Sales - In-Person; MP - Speaking Engagement
Usages: Automation platform flow (3); Report (13); Sales view (5)

Name: Attached file IDs
Description: The IDs of the files that are attached to the engagement

Name: Activity created by
Description: The user who created the engagement

Name: Create date
Description: The date that an engagement was created
Usages: Rollup property (3); Inbounddb lists (1); Automation platform flow (5); Report (21); Dataset (3); Sales view (5)

Name: Last modified date
Description: The date any property on this engagement was modified

Name: Activity date
Description: The date that an engagement occurred
Usages: Rollup property (5); Report (7); Sales view (3); Dashboard (1)

Name: Activity assigned to
Description: The user that the activity is assigned to in HubSpot. This can be any HubSpot user or Salesforce integration user, and can be set manually or via Workflows.
Usages: Inbounddb lists (1); Automation platform flow (1); Report (41); Sales view (8); Dashboard (1)

Name: HubSpot Team
Description: The team of the owner of an engagement.

Name: Talking points
Options: America Prays 250; NRB 2026; PRAY Science (Pray Science)

Name: HubSpot attendee owner IDs
Description: Stores the owner ids of any attendees who are users in the portal
Usages: Inbounddb lists (4); Automation platform flow (1); Report (1)

Name: Contact first outreach date
Description: The first outreach date of the associated contact

Name: Internal Meeting Notes
Description: The internal notes from the meeting
Usages: Automation platform flow (4); Report (3); Sales view (5)

Name: Meeting description
Description: The text description of the meeting
Usages: Automation platform flow (3); Report (2); Sales view (8)

Name: Meeting end time
Description: The date when the meeting ends
Usages: Calculated property (1); Rollup property (3); Sales view (3)

Name: Meeting location
Description: Where the meeting takes place

Name: Location type
Description: The type of location for the meeting event
Options: Phone call (PHONE); Address (ADDRESS); Custom (CUSTOM); Video Conference (VCE)

Name: Meeting outcome
Description: The outcome of this meeting
Options: Scheduled (SCHEDULED); Completed (COMPLETED); Rescheduled (RESCHEDULED); No Show (NO_SHOW); Canceled (CANCELED); Completed Onsite (COMPLETED ONSITE)
Usages: Inbounddb lists (9); Automation platform flow (6); Report (28); Dataset (3); Sales view (4)

Name: Meeting source
Description: The source where the meeting was booked
Options: CRM UI (CRM_UI); Integration (INTEGRATION); Meeting created from a proposed time (AVAILABILITY_SCHEDULE); Meeting created on calendar from CRM (BIDIRECTIONAL_API); Meeting synced from calendar to CRM (BIDIRECTIONAL_SYNC); Meetings (Embedded) (MEETINGS_EMBEDDED); Meetings (Public) (MEETINGS_PUBLIC)
Usages: Rollup property (3); Automation platform flow (1); Report (8); Sales view (5)

Name: Meeting start time
Description: The date when the meeting starts
Usages: Calculated property (1); Rollup property (5); Inbounddb lists (10); Automation platform flow (7); Report (52); Dataset (1); Sales view (8)

Name: Meeting name
Description: The title of the meeting
Usages: Rollup property (1); Automation platform flow (6); Report (13); Dataset (1); Sales view (8)

Name: Outcome canceled count
Description: 1 if outcome is canceled otherwise 0

Name: Outcome completed count
Description: 1 if outcome is completed otherwise 0

Name: Outcome no show count
Description: 1 if outcome is no-show otherwise 0

Name: Outcome rescheduled count
Description: 1 if outcome is rescheduled otherwise 0

Name: Outcome scheduled count
Description: 1 if outcome is scheduled otherwise 0

Name: Time to book meeting from first contact
Description: The time it took to book a meeting from first outreach date of the associated contact

Name: Video conference platform
Description: The video conference platform (Zoom, Teams, or Google Meet) that the video conference URL (hs_video_conference_url) is hosted on
Options: Google Meet (google_meet); Zoom (zoom); Microsoft Teams (microsoft_teams); Other (other)

Name: Video conference url
Description: Optional property storing the video conference url for an online meeting

Name: Meeting Tag
Options: Inbound - Paid (Inbound); Inbound - Organic; IG Outreach; Live Events

Name: Associated Contact Source
Options: Organic Search (ORGANIC_SEARCH); Paid Search (PAID_SEARCH); Email Marketing (EMAIL_MARKETING); Organic Social (SOCIAL_MEDIA); Referrals (REFERRALS); Other Campaigns (OTHER_CAMPAIGNS); Direct Traffic (DIRECT_TRAFFIC); Offline Sources (OFFLINE); Paid Social (PAID_SOCIAL); AI Referrals (AI_REFERRALS)

Name: Created by user ID
Description: The user who created this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Merged record IDs
Description: The list of record IDs that have been merged into this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Record ID
Description: The unique ID for this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.
Usages: Rollup property (1); Report (32); Dataset (4); Pipeline object tag (1)

Name: Record source detail 1
Description: First level of detail on how this record was created.

Name: Record source detail 2
Description: Second level of detail on how this record was created.

Name: Record source detail 3
Description: Third level of detail on how this record was created.

Name: Record source
Description: How this record was created.

Name: Updated by user ID
Description: The user who last updated this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.
